<div>
  <h2 align="center" style="text-align:center;"><span style="line-height:115%; font-size:24.0pt; ">CONTRAT</span><span style="font-size:24.0pt; "> D&rsquo;ACHAT DU compte MARCHAND <span style="color:red; ">MCNP</span></span></h2>
</div>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; "><br clear="all" style="page-break-before:always;">
</span>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Entre&nbsp; les soussignés:</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">ESMC (Entreprise Sociale de Marché Commun) SARL U au  capital de 1&nbsp;000&nbsp;000 F CFA&nbsp;; Siège social&nbsp;: Lomé(TOGO),  Nukafu, Angle rue Sagouda, Kiyéou et Bandjéli BP 30038, immatriculé au RCCM  sous le numéro TG-LOM 2014 B514, représenté par son Gérant Monsieur Essohamlon  SAMA </span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; "> Ci-après dénommée «  le Vendeur»,</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">D&rsquo;une part</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Et</span></p>
<ul>
  <li><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">La collectivité    […………………………………………]</span></li>
</ul>
<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<ul>
  <li><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">LA SOCIETE […………………………………………] au capital de  [……………..]Immatriculée au RCCM, sous le numéro [………………..], dont le siège social  est [……….], représentée par [………………..] dûment habilité aux fins des présentes  /   Ou</span></li>
</ul>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<ul>
  <li><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Personnes physique (référence………………….)</span></li>
</ul>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Ci-après dénommée «l&rsquo;acheteur»,</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">D&rsquo;autre part</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify;"><span style="line-height:115%; font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Il  est convenu ce qui suit&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">:</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify;"><strong><u><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Article 1</span></u></strong><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;: <strong><u>Objet</u></strong></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:35.4pt;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">1.1: <u>Pour la collectivité</u></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Ce contrat s&rsquo;entend dans le cadre de l&rsquo;exploitation collective  du Compte Marchand d&rsquo;administration </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">MCNP </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">(Marché de Crédit en Nature Pérenne) pour toute  collectivité organisée d&rsquo;aval en amont. Les collectivités ici désignées sont  les entités qui représentent la communauté dans le cadre de son développement  sans-laissés pour compte impliquant toutes les factions économiques d&rsquo;une  communauté qui s&rsquo;agrège à l&rsquo;organisation d&rsquo;aval en amont dans un pays. </span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; color:black; ">Exemple de communauté organisée&nbsp;: les Communautés de  Développement de Village(CDV), les Communautés de Développement de Quartier  (CDQ). </span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:35.4pt;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">1.2&nbsp;: <u>Pour les personnes  physiques et morales</u></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><u><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; "><span style="text-decoration:none; ">&nbsp;</span></span></u></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Ce contrat tient lieu d&rsquo;acquisition du Compte Marchand </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">MCNP</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; "> (Marché de Crédit en Nature Pérenne)  pour toute personne physique ou morale.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">La caractéristique du compte marchand est son  interdépendance au sein de la communauté. </span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify;"><strong><u><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Article 2</span></u></strong><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;: <strong><u>Caractéristiques du </u></strong></span><strong><u><span style="line-height:115%; font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">MCNP</span></u></strong><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; "> </span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:35.4pt;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">2.1&nbsp;: <u>Définition</u></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Le </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">MCNP </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">est  le progiciel conçu pour la gestion de la solvabilité intégrée des transactions  marchandes entre acteurs offreurs et demandeurs du marché global.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Le progiciel </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">MCNP</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; "> est porteur de Compte Marchand&nbsp;: personne physique  et morale qui s&rsquo;acquiert par voie d&rsquo;achat mais n&rsquo;est pas transmissible.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:35.4pt;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">2.2&nbsp;: <u>Particularité</u></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Le Compte Marchand </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">MCNP </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">est le compte servant pour toute Personne</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Physique ou Morale à investir,</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:yellow; "> </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; ">à travailler contre salaire, à vendre et à acheter  grâce aux unités numériques émises par le <span style="color:red; ">MCNP</span>.  Ces <span style="color:black; ">unités sont le pouvoir d&rsquo;achat, contrepartie de  la monnaie bancaire dépensée par toute personne physique ou morale acteur du </span><span style="color:red; ">MCNP</span><span style="color:black; ">. La monnaie bancaire dépensée  pour l&rsquo;acquisition des unités forme le Fonds qui Garantit le</span><span style="color:yellow; "> </span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Financement en Nature(FGFN), caution du Marché de Crédit  en Nature Pérenne.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:35.4pt;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">2.3&nbsp;: <u>Structure et  organisation du compte marchand</u></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><u><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; "><span style="text-decoration:none; ">&nbsp;</span></span></u></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Les Comptes Marchands Personnes Morales se regroupent en  divisions selon leur produit spécifique. Il y a les Comptes Marchands qui  vendent appelés Opérateurs Economiques et ceux qui ne vendent pas appelés Opérateurs  Socio – Economiques.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">On distingue deux sortes de divisions&nbsp;: </span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">- </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">les divisions qui administrent le </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">MCNP </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">et</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">- </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">les divisions qui animent le </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">MCNP</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Les divisions s&rsquo;organisent en Créneaux Producteurs,  Transformateurs et Distributeurs et regroupent :</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">- </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">la Filière,</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">- </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">l&rsquo;ACNEV (Achat Crédit en Nature Entrepôt et Ventes),</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">- </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">la Technopole,</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">- </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">les Grossistes,</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">- </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">les Semi – Grossistes et</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">- </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">les Détaillants.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Le Compte Marchand Personne Physique est le compte de tout  individu sur le </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">MCNP</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify;"><strong><u><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Article 3</span></u></strong><strong><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;: <u>Conditions générales</u></span></strong></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Peuvent acheter le Compte Marchand les personnes morales et les personnes  physiques qui adhèrent au mode d&rsquo;entreprendre de L&rsquo;Economie Sociale de Marché  Commun (ESMC)/</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">MCNP </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">dont les conditions sont les suivantes  :</span></p>
<ul>
  <li><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; "> Accepter que le Revenu Périodique Garanti  pérenne pour tous entretenu par le travail productif sur le marché </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">MCNP </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">soit un investissement&nbsp;;</span></li>
  <li><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; "> Accepter le mode de payement en nature géré  par la comptabilité intégrée au progiciel </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">MCNP </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">dont la constitution du Fonds qui Garantit le Financement  en Nature (FGFN) est le gage&nbsp;;</span></li>
  <li><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Accepter la solvabilité absolue de  l&rsquo;Humain par la monétisation du travail productif dont il est porteur&nbsp;;</span></li>
  <li><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; "> Accepter que l&rsquo;employé soit entrepreneur et  que l&rsquo;entrepreneur soit employé vis-à-vis des responsabilités de l&rsquo;entreprise  qui bénéficie du crédit productif, Crédit en Nature Convertible Salaire (</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">CNCS</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">) et de l&rsquo;investissement en nature (</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">I</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">) sur le </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">MCNP&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">;</span></li>
  <li><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Production et consommation respectant  la nature&nbsp;;</span></li>
  <li><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Solvabilité absolue assurée par la  compensation en nature entre Divisions organisées comme suit : Filière,  Technopole, ACNEV, Grossistes, Semi-grossistes et Détaillants dans les créneaux  Producteur, Transformateur et Distributeur&nbsp;;</span></li>
  <li><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Production et consommation respectant  l&rsquo;économie d&rsquo;usage qui avorte l&rsquo;épargne et la thésaurisation&nbsp;;</span></li>
  <li><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Production et consommation respectant  l&rsquo;économie de service qui implique l&rsquo;achat de services plutôt que  l&rsquo;achat-possession&nbsp;;</span></li>
  <li><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Production et consommation respectant  l&rsquo;économie circulaire qui implique le renouvelable et le recyclable plutôt que  l&rsquo;économie linéaire (consommer et jeter)&nbsp;;</span></li>
  <li><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Production et consommation respectant  l&rsquo;économie de circuit court (produire localement) et de cycle court (formation  et apprentissage brefs ou accélérés)&nbsp;;</span></li>
  <li><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Respecter les principes, les  conventions ESMC et les normes d&rsquo;utilisation du progiciel </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">MCNP</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">.</span></li>
</ul>
<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpLast" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify;"><strong><u><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Article 4</span></u></strong><strong><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;: <u>Conditions spécifiques liées à l&rsquo;achat d&rsquo;un compte marchand</u></span></strong></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">            4.1&nbsp;: <u>Cout (Adhésion)</u></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">L&rsquo;achat du Compte Marchand </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">MCNP </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">est  conditionné par le versement des frais suivants :</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:35.4pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:35.4pt;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">4.1.1&nbsp;: <u>Personnes physiques</u></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">- </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Frais de Solvabilité à (montant) : ……………………………………………. FCFA</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">- </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Frais de Licence à (montant)       : …………………..……………..………… FCFA</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;margin-left:62.4pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:8.4pt;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; "> 4.1.2&nbsp;: <u>Personnes  morales</u></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">- Frais de Solvabilité à (montant) : …………………………………………….  FCFA</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">- </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Frais de Licence à (montant)      : ……………………………………….…… FCFA</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;margin-left:35.4pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:35.4pt;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">4.2&nbsp;: <u>Résiliation du contrat</u></span><u><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; "> </span></u><u><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; "> </span></u></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:35.4pt;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><u><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; "><span style="text-decoration:none; ">&nbsp;</span></span></u></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Les parties sont libres de résilier le contrat.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Toutefois, les frais payés à l&rsquo;ouverture du compte ne sont  pas remboursables. </span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">L&rsquo;utilisation du Compte Marchand désengage entièrement le vendeur  du compte et le bénéficiaire de frais de solvabilité de toute responsabilité  découlant de l&rsquo;usage qu&rsquo;en font les détenteurs.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><strong><u><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Article  5</span></u></strong><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">: <strong><u>Durée</u></strong></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Ce contrat est à durée indéterminé.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><strong><u><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Article  6</span></u></strong><strong><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;: <u>Lieu d&rsquo;exécution du </u></span></strong><strong><u><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">MCNP</span></u></strong><strong><u><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; "> </span></u></strong></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><strong><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Les opérations liées au </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">MCNP</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; "> pourront s&rsquo;opérer sur l&rsquo;ensemble du Territoire National.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><strong><u><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Article  7</span></u></strong><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">: <strong><u>Avantages liés à l&rsquo;ouverture de compte marchand</u></strong></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Le Compte Marchand </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">MCNP </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">permet à son détenteur d&rsquo;obtenir les avantages suivants :</span></p>
<ul>
  <li><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">l&rsquo;Achat du Pouvoir d&rsquo;Achat </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:#00B1F1; ">CNP&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">;</span></li>
  <li><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">le Bail Nue – Propriété (BNP),  c&rsquo;est-à-dire au prêt financier ou bancaire cautionné par le </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:#00B1F1; ">CNP&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">;</span></li>
  <li><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">l&rsquo;investissement </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:#00B0F0; ">nrPRE</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;;</span></li>
  <li><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">l&rsquo;emploi social marchand rémunéré en  unités </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">MCNP </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">dites  Crédit en Nature Convertible Salaire (</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">CNCS</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">)&nbsp;;</span></li>
  <li><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">l&rsquo;enrôlement des entreprises et  industries à l&rsquo;investissement alloué en unités </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">MCNP </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">dites Subvention Marchande des Coûts d&rsquo;Investissement et  de Production Nouvelle (</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">SMCIPN</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">).  La </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">SMCIPN </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">est  composée de l&rsquo;investissement qui rembourse les biens immédiats consommés par  les entreprises et industries auprès d&rsquo;autres entreprises et industries ainsi  que le salaire qui rémunère les forces de production (travailleurs du social  marchand).</span></li>
</ul>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><strong><u><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Article  8</span></u></strong><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;: <strong><u>Les obligations du détenteur du Compte Marchand </u></strong></span><strong><u><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">MCNP</span></u></strong><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; "> </span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:35.4pt;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">8.1&nbsp;: <u>Obligations liées aux personnes  physiques</u></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">La Personne Physique titulaire du Compte Marchand </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">MCNP </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">est seule responsable de la gestion  de son Compte et est garante de la productivité de sa communauté. A cet effet,  elle dispose de l&rsquo;outil d&rsquo;enrôlement dit </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:#00B0F0; ">nrPRE  Kit Technopole </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">pour :</span></p>
<ul>
  <li><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">s&rsquo;éduquer,</span></li>
  <li><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">apprendre,</span></li>
  <li><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">se former,</span></li>
  <li><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">faire les stages,</span></li>
  <li><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">se recycler,</span></li>
  <li><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">faire des recherches visant le  développement,</span></li>
  <li><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">s&rsquo;enrôler à l&rsquo;emploi dans l&rsquo;une au  moins des divisions au service de l&rsquo;industrialisation du travail sur le </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">MCNP</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">.</span></li>
</ul>
<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpLast" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Elle est garante en dernier ressort de la solvabilité  absolue et pérenne, de la liquidité absolue ainsi que de la disponibilité  absolue du travail sur le marché </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">MCNP, </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">dans le respect des normes du modèle de l&rsquo;Economie Universelle(EU)  liées, aux modalités de paiement en réponse aux attentes de sa communauté.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:35.4pt;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">8.2&nbsp;: <u>Obligations liées aux Personnes  Morales</u></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Concernant les Personnes Morales regroupées en divisions  (division administratrice et division animatrice du </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">MCNP</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">), leurs obligations sont les suivantes  :</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;margin-left:35.4pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:35.4pt;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">8.2.1&nbsp;: <u>Pour la FILIERE</u></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">La Filière tout comme l&rsquo;ACNEV et la Technopole sont les  trois entités, têtes de division qui agréent la mise sur chaîne des Entreprises  et Industries membres et partenaires dans leurs Créneaux : Production, Transformation  et Distribution composé chacun de Grossistes, Semi-Grossistes et</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Détaillants grâce au Compte Marchand d&rsquo;administration Filière.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Elle est garante en dernier ressort sur le marché </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">MCNP</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">:</span></p>
<ul>
  <li><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">de la liquidité absolue de son Bien,  Produit et Service,</span></li>
  <li><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">de la disponibilité absolue de son  Bien, Produit et Service, (la liquidité et la disponibilité absolues qui sous  entendent que la qualité et la quantité du Bien, du Produit et Service sont  gage de la solvabilité absolue et pérenne de ladite Filière),</span></li>
  <li><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">du respect des règles de gestion, des  normes de l&rsquo;économie circulaire, de l&rsquo;économie d&rsquo;usage, de l&rsquo;économie de  service et de l&rsquo;économie de cycle court, ainsi que le respect des normes du  modèle EU liées aux modalités de paiement,</span></li>
  <li><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">de la réponse aux attentes du </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">MCNP </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">face à la division.</span></li>
</ul>
<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpLast" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:35.4pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:35.4pt;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">8.2.2&nbsp;: <u>Pour l&rsquo;ACNEV</u></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">L&rsquo;ACNEV tout comme la Filière et la Technopole sont les  trois entités, têtes de division qui agréent la mise sur chaîne des Entreprises  et Industries membres et partenaires dans leurs Créneaux : Production, Transformation  et Distribution composé chacun de Grossistes, Semi-Grossistes et Détaillants  grâce au Compte Marchand d&rsquo;administration ACNEV.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">L&rsquo;ACNEV se charge de l&rsquo;achat des intrants, de la  centralisation des demandes et des ventes du BPS (Biens, Produits, Services) de  la division sur le marché </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">MCNP </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">dans le respect des normes du modèle EU (Economie  Universelle) liées aux modalités de paiement.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Il est garant en dernier ressort :</span></p>
<ul>
  <li><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">de la solvabilité absolue et pérenne  de son BPS,</span></li>
  <li><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">de la liquidité absolue de son BPS,</span></li>
  <li><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">de la disponibilité absolue de son  BPS sur le marché </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">MCNP </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">dans  le respect des normes du modèle EU en réponse aux attentes du </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">MCNP </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">face à la division.</span></li>
</ul>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;margin-left:35.4pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:35.4pt;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">8.2.3&nbsp;: <u>Pour la TECHNOPOLE</u></span></p>
<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">La Technopole tout comme la Filière et l&rsquo;ACNEV sont les  trois entités, têtes de division qui agréent la mise sur chaîne des Entreprises  et Industries membres et partenaires dans leurs Créneaux : Production,  Transformation et Distribution composé chacun de Grossistes, Semi-Grossistes et</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Détaillants grâce au Compte Marchand d&rsquo;administration  Technopole.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Pour la sécurité de tous sur le </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">MCNP</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">, tout titulaire de Compte Marchand  est responsable de toute utilisation de ses moyens d&rsquo;authentification  (biométrie et cartes) ainsi que du rôle pour lequel le compte lui est affecté.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">La Technopole est garante:</span></p>
<ul>
  <li><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">de l&rsquo;éducation,</span></li>
  <li><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">de l&rsquo;apprentissage,</span></li>
  <li><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">de la formation,</span></li>
  <li><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">des stages,</span></li>
  <li><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">du recyclage,</span></li>
  <li><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">des recherches et développement, </span></li>
  <li><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">du plein emploi de la division au  service de l&rsquo;industrialisation du BPS sur le marché </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">MCNP </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">dans le respect des normes du modèle  EU liées aux modalités de paiement.</span></li>
</ul>
<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpLast" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Elle est garante en dernier ressort de la solvabilité  absolue et pérenne, de la liquidité absolue ainsi que de la disponibilité  absolue du BPS sur le marché</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">MCNP </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">dans le respect des normes du modèle  EU en réponse aux attentes du </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">MCNP </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">face à la division.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><strong><u><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Article  9</span></u></strong><strong><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;: <u>Descriptif des unités </u></span></strong><strong><u><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">MCNP</span></u></strong></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><u><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; "><span style="text-decoration:none; ">&nbsp;</span></span></u></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Les unités </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">MCNP </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">sont les titres privatifs de solvabilité qui se regroupent  en deux principales catégories : le pouvoir d&rsquo;achat appelé Crédit en Nature  Prépayé(</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:#00B1F1; ">CNP</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">)  et le crédit productif appelé Crédit en Nature Convertible Salaire (</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">CNCS</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">).</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><u><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; "><span style="text-decoration:none; ">&nbsp;</span></span></u></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:35.4pt;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">9.1&nbsp;: <u>Le Crédit en Nature  Prépayé (</u></span><u><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:#00B1F1; ">CNP</span></u><u><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">)</span></u><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; "> </span></p>
<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Le </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:#00B1F1; ">CNP </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">est  le Titre Privatif Numérique qui fait office de pouvoir d&rsquo;achat libérateur,  c&rsquo;est-à-dire soldé d&rsquo;avance par le bénéficiaire sur le </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">MCNP</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Cependant, le </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:#00B1F1; ">CNP </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">est la créance du </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">MCNP </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">à solder en nature grâce à l&rsquo;usage du titre privatif de  solvabilité </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">CNCS </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">qui  lui, fait office de crédit productif.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Le Titre </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:#00B1F1; ">CNP </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">peut être récurrent ou non récurrent.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">C&rsquo;est le </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:#00B1F1; ">CNP </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">qui permet de former le Fonds qui Garantit le Financement  en</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Nature (FGFN) nominal non décaissable, tandis que le </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">CNCS </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">permet de former le FGFN réel&nbsp;:  Biens, Produits et Services&nbsp;; c&rsquo;est-à-dire que le </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">CNCS </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">est la rémunération des forces  productrices des entreprises et industries contre les Biens, Produits et  Services (BPS).</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Le FGFN en ses deux versions (nominal et réel) est le gage  du </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">MCNP </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">vis-à-vis  de tout partenaire bancaire et financier ainsi que de tout fournisseur extérieur  de Biens, Produits et Services.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Le Titre </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:#00B1F1; ">CNP </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">peut être récurrent ou non récurrent.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;margin-left:35.4pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:35.4pt;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">9.1.1&nbsp;: <u>Le crédit en Nature Prépayé  récurrent (</u></span><u><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:#00B0F0; ">CNPr</span></u><u><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">)</span></u></p>
<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Le </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:#00B1F1; ">CNPr </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">est  un revenu récurrent affecté directement aux BPS. Son prix d&rsquo;achat est fonction  de la Période de Constitution du Capital (PCK) aujourd&rsquo;hui à 5.6. La PCK peut  varier. L&rsquo;achat du </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:#00B1F1; ">CNPr </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">est  un débours et le </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:#00B1F1; ">CNPr </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">ne  se cumule pas mais se renouvelle à chaque période de façon illimitée.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Cependant, le cumul du </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:#00B1F1; ">CNPr </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">est autorisé en cas de suspension de son renouvellement pérenne  par le titulaire. A cet effet, le cumul observe le renouvellement pendant la période  PCK pour la reconstitution en unité́ NN et PRK pour la reconstitution en  nature.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">La période de renouvellement est de trente jours à ce jour.  Elle peut varier en fonction du niveau de solvabilité sur le </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">MCNP</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">, c&rsquo;est-à-dire en fonction de la capacité  de production effective des BPS.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">La version </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:#00B1F1; ">CNPr </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">dont le renouvellement est limité est destinée d&rsquo;une part  aux entreprises et industries (douze fois à ce jour) et d&rsquo;autre part aux  ménages, variable selon le cas du </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:#00B1F1; ">kit  Technopole nrPRE</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">. Le </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:#00B1F1; ">CNPr </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">limité ne se reconstitue qu&rsquo;en cas de non expression. Il  ne peut être disponible qu&rsquo;après l&rsquo;observation des douze périodes de  renouvellement.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;margin-left:35.4pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:35.4pt;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">9.1.2: <u>Le crédit en nature Prépayé non récurrent  (</u></span><u><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:#00B1F1; ">CNPnr</span></u><u><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">)</span></u></p>
<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Le Crédit en Nature Prépayé non récurrent (</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:#00B1F1; ">CNPnr</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">) est la version  non renouvelable du Crédit en Nature Prépayé récurrent. Contrairement au </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:#00B1F1; ">CNPr</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">, le </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:#00B1F1; ">CNPnr </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">s&rsquo;obtient de façon  cumulée, non renouvelable et vise la réduction des coûts des BPS aux  bénéficiaires. Le </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:#00B1F1; ">CNPnr </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">désigne le </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:#00B1F1; ">RPGnr </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">et l&rsquo;</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:#00B0F0; ">Inr.</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; "> </span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">On distingue à cet effet, le </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:#00B1F1; ">CNPnrPRK </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">et le </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:#00B1F1; ">CNPnrPRE</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">. En fonction de  ses variables PRK et PRE, le </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:#00B1F1; ">CNPnr </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">se</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:#00B1F1; "> </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">reconstitue  par simple voie de conversion en d&rsquo;autres unités sur le </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">MCNP</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;margin-left:35.4pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">9.2&nbsp;: <u>Le Crédit en Nature Convertible Salaire(</u></span><u><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">CNCS</span></u><u><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">)</span></u><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; "> </span></p>
<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;margin-left:35.4pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:35.4pt;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">9.2.1&nbsp;: <u>Le Crédit en Nature Convertible Salaire non  récurrent (</u></span><u><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">CNCSnr</span></u><u><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">)</span></u><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; "> </span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Le Crédit en Nature Convertible Salaire non récurrent (</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">CNCSnr</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">) est le Titre</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Privatif de Solvabilité des salariés (forces de  production) qui s&rsquo;obtient par voie d&rsquo;achat par les employeurs secteurs public  et privé pour le compte de leurs salariés. Il est la contrepartie du travail  effectif fourni aux entreprises et industries qui l&rsquo;ont acheté.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Le </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">CNCSnr </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">aux  mains des salariés est destiné à l&rsquo;achat des Titres Privatifs</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:#00B1F1; ">CNPnr</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">. Le </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">CNCSnr </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">doit observer la  période de maturité. Il peut cependant s&rsquo;échanger librement (contre toute  offre) sur le marché en ligne du </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">MCNP</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;margin-left:35.4pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:35.4pt;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">9.2.2&nbsp;: <u>Le Crédit en Nature Convertible Salaire  récurrent (</u></span><u><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">CNCSr</span></u><u><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">)</span></u></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Le Crédit en Nature Convertible Salaire récurrent (</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">CNCSr</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">) est le Titre</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Privatif de Solvabilité des salariés (forces de  production) qui s&rsquo;obtient par voie de la </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">SMCPN </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">pour le cas du salaire social. Il est la contrepartie du travail  effectif fourni aux entreprises et industries qui l&rsquo;ont acquis.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Conservé auprès de l&rsquo;employeur, le </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">CNCSr </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">ne se transforme pas et peut être utilisé  à tout moment.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Le </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">CNCSr </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">aux  mains des salariés est destiné à l&rsquo;achat des Titres Privatifs</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:#00B1F1; ">CNPnr</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">. Dans ce cas, il  doit observer la période de maturité. Mature ou non, le </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">CNCS </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">peut s&rsquo;échanger librement (contre  toute offre) sur le marché en ligne du </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">MCNP</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><strong><u><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Article  10&nbsp;</span></u></strong><strong><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">: <u>Cas de force majeure</u></span></strong></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><strong><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">En cas de force majeure qui empêcherait l&rsquo;une au moins des parties  de remplir ses obligations aux termes du présent contrat, les parties ne seront  pas responsables des conséquences de l&rsquo;inexécution ou d&rsquo;une exécution tardive  de leurs obligations si celles-ci résultaient du cas de force majeure.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Quel que soit le cas de force majeure, le recommencement  reste l&rsquo;ultime recours auquel doivent se fier les propriétaires de compte  marchand.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Les titulaires du compte marchand sont codétenteurs du  progiciel </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">MCNP</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">. </span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">A cet effet, le moyen de production étant le progiciel </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">MCNP</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">, sa remise en exploitation sera  toujours disponible, de mêmes que les données de sauvegarde. </span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><strong><u><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Article  11</span></u></strong><strong><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;: <u>Règlement de litige lié à l&rsquo;utilisation du compte marchand </u></span></strong><strong><u><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">MCNP</span></u></strong></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Il faut préciser que des litiges entre les différents  utilisateurs du compte marchand </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">MCNP</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; "> pourraient survenir. C&rsquo;est dans ce cadre qu&rsquo;un dispositif  de règlement de litige à l&rsquo;interne a été mis en place sur la plateforme.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Ce dispositif est le triple compte marchand de  surveillance que sont&nbsp;: le Compte Marchand Détentrice, le Compte Marchand Surveillance  et le Compte Marchand Exécutante qui gèrent les sous comptes marchands de  réglementation, d&rsquo;audit-contrôle, des alertes, des assurances, de protection  qui forment en soi des instruments internes de règlements de litiges.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;margin-left:0cm;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Les  avantages liés à la mise en place de ce dispositif porte sur l&rsquo;efficacité des  règlements axés sur la solvabilité intégrée à la plateforme </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">MCNP</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;; étant entendu que tout litige  auquel allusion est faite se résume au défaut de paiement ou à la non  solvabilité les uns vis-à-vis des autres sur la plateforme.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Cependant, le </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">MCNP</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; "> étant un Marché de Crédit en Nature Pérenne, aucune  créance n&rsquo;est due en espèce bancaire et reste en nature. Il n&rsquo;existe que les Biens,  Produits et services réels en demande qui soldent de façon absolue les  redevances.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">En signant, ce contrat, l&rsquo;utilisateur accepte les  principes, les conventions ESMC et les normes d&rsquo;utilisation du progiciel </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">MCNP </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; "> inscrits dans le présent contrat et s&rsquo;engage à  respecter toutes les conditions liées à l&rsquo;usage de son compte marchand.  </span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><strong><u><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Article  12</span></u></strong><strong><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;: <u>Dispositions particulières relatives aux têtes de divisions Exécutantes</u></span></strong></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Les conventions qui suivent sont liées à l&rsquo;utilisation du compte  marchand </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">MCNP</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Elles définissent, cependant, les clauses internes entre les  différentes têtes de divisions existantes sur la plateforme et leurs membres ou  partenaires en vue d&rsquo;asseoir toutes les bases de la solvabilité requise.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><strong><u><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; "><span style="text-decoration:none; ">&nbsp;</span></span></u></strong></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><strong><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">12.1 Convention N°  1 :</span></strong></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Entre les structures Têtes de Division Exécutante  Partenaires Bancaires et Financiers (S-CM Exécutante PBF), d&rsquo;une part </span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">et</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Les Acteurs Consommateurs du </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">MCNP</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">, d&rsquo;autre part</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Il est convenu ce qui suit :</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Dans le but de former continuellement le déposit et le DAT  convenus avec</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">les PBF, les structures ESMC têtes de Division PBF se  mettent d&rsquo;accord avec les acteurs consommateurs du marché (individus, ménages, institutions,  entreprises et industries) pour consommer permanemment les marchandises auprès  des Distributeurs-Fournisseurs. </span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">En guise d&rsquo;optimisation du pouvoir d&rsquo;achat des  consommateurs, les modalités de consommation convenues sont la consommation  récurrente et la consommation non récurrente.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Le capital d&rsquo;achat variable de ces deux pouvoirs d&rsquo;achat de  consommation</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">se fait 5,6 fois la consommation périodique pour le  récurrent et 5,6(1/8) fois la consommation une fois de bon pour le non  récurrent.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><strong><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">12.2 <u>Convention  N° 2 :</u></span></strong></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Entre les structures Têtes de Division Exécutante  Partenaires</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Bancaires et Financiers (S-CM Exécutante PBF), d&rsquo;une part</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; "> et </span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Les Partenaires Bancaires et Financiers du </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">MCNP</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">, d&rsquo;autre part</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; "> Il est convenu ce  qui suit :</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Les structures ESMC Têtes de Division Exécutante (S-CM  Exécutante PBF) se mettent d&rsquo;accord avec les Partenaires Bancaires et  Financiers du marché pour acheter continuellement les créances de leurs divers  produits financiers (les escomptes des traites aux Distributeurs-Fournisseurs  du marché et les crédits divers accordés aux clients) à condition que les  bénéficiaires de ces produits financiers fassent en retour toutes leurs  dépenses de consommation et de production sur le </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">MCNP</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">La modalité convenue est celle du paiement par traites aux  fournisseurs dont l&rsquo;escompte par les banques est payé par échéance à ces dernières.  A titre d&rsquo;exemple, 8 échéances par unité de traite escomptée et 22,4 échéances  pour tous crédits faits aux membres en vue du financement de leur capital  d&rsquo;achat du pouvoir d&rsquo;achat.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Pour cela, les structures ESMC Têtes de Division  Exécutante (S-CM</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Exécutante PBF) s&rsquo;engagent à former la garantie FGFN en  guise de DAT en dehors du déposit.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Cependant, il est obtenu des Partenaires Bancaires et  Financiers dans le cadre du marché commun le procédé de l&rsquo;achat en retour des  biens, produits et services de leurs consommations usuelles auprès des  structures</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">ESMC Têtes de Division Exécutante (S-CM Exécutante BPS),  grâce à leurs  intérêts et frais divers  perçus sur le </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">MCNP</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">.</span></p>
<span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; "><br clear="all" style="page-break-before:always;">
</span>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><strong><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">12.3 <u>Convention  N° 3 :</u></span></strong></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Entre les structures Têtes de Division Exécutante  Subvention</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Marchande des Coûts de Production Nouvelle (S-CM  Exécutante </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">SMCPN</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">),  d&rsquo;une part</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">et </span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Les Acteurs salariés du </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">MCNP</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">, d&rsquo;autre part </span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Il est convenu ce qui suit :</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Les structures ESMC Têtes de Division Exécutante (S-CM  Exécutante</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">SMCPN</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">) se  mettent d&rsquo;accord avec les acteurs salariés des trois créneaux&nbsp;:  Producteurs, Transformateurs et Distributeurs du marché pour continuellement  rémunérer leur travail effectivement accompli, à condition que la rémunération  serve à la consommation récurrente et non récurrente sur le </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">MCNP</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><strong><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">12.4 <u>Convention  N° 4 :</u></span></strong></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><strong><u><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; "><span style="text-decoration:none; ">&nbsp;</span></span></u></strong></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Entre les structures Têtes de Division Exécutante  Subvention</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Marchande des Coûts d&rsquo;Investissement (S-CM Exécutante </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">SMCI</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">), d&rsquo;une part</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">et </span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Les Producteurs-Transformateurs des BPS du </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">MCNP</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">, d&rsquo;autre part</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Il est convenu ce qui suit :</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Les structures ESMC Têtes de Division Exécutante  Subvention Marchande des Coûts d&rsquo;Investissement (S-CM Exécutante </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">SMCI</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">) se mettent d&rsquo;accord avec les  Producteurs-Transformateurs des BPS du marché pour commander continuellement  les marchandises destinées aux réapprovisionnements des  Distributeurs-Fournisseurs. </span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">La condition convenue est que les  Producteurs-Transformateurs obtiennent la </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">SMCI</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; "> pour acheter en retour les BPS auprès des Distributeurs-  Fournisseurs des BPS de consommation industrielle pour répondre aux commandes.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><strong><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">12.5 <u>Convention  N° 5 :</u></span></strong></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Entre les structures Têtes de Division Exécutante Sous-Compte</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Marchand Exécutante Biens, Produits et Services (S-CM Exécutante  BPS), d&rsquo;une part</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">et </span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Les Distributeurs-Fournisseurs des BPS du </span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">MCNP</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">, d&rsquo;autre part</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Il est convenu ce qui suit :</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Les structures ESMC Têtes de Division Exécutante (S-CM  Exécutante BPS) se mettent d&rsquo;accord avec les Distributeurs-Fournisseurs des BPS  du marché pour acheter continuellement leurs marchandises à condition que  ceux-ci achètent en retour leurs marchandises en guise de réapprovisionnement  auprès des structures ESMC Têtes de Division Exécutante (S-CM</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Exécutante BPS).</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">La modalité convenue est celle du paiement par traites (8  traites par exemple). Pour cela, les structures ESMC Têtes de Division  Exécutante (S-CM Exécutante BPS) s&rsquo;engagent à faire avaliser lesdites traites  par les banques en guise de garantie. </span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">Cependant, l&rsquo;exigibilité des redevances aux  Distributeurs-Fournisseurs est et reste le procédé de l&rsquo;achat de BPS en retour  auprès des structures ESMC Têtes de Division Exécutante (S-CM Exécutante BPS).</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; ">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify;"><strong><em><u><span style="line-height:115%; font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; ">Article 13</span></u></em></strong><strong><em><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; ">&nbsp;:<u> DISPOSITIONS FINALES </u></span></em></strong></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; ">Au vu de tout ce qui précède et étant donné que la disponibilité des  unités incombe aux divisions administratrices, que la disponibilité de l&rsquo;espèce  bancaire incombe à la division PBF et que la disponibilité des BPS incombe aux  divisions animatrices, la disponibilité des unités, de l&rsquo;espèce bancaire et des  BPS n&rsquo;incombe nullement au vendeur de Compte Marchand et de la licence <strong><span style="color:red; ">MCNP</span></strong>. </span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:12.0pt;text-align:justify;"><strong><em><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; ">En effet, la liquidité des unités, la liquidité de l&rsquo;espèce  bancaire et la disponibilité des BPS sont exclusivement de la responsabilité  des têtes de Divisions&nbsp;: Filières, Technopoles, ACNEV et même de la  personne physique, chapeautés par les divisions de l&rsquo;Exécutante, de la  Surveillance et de la Détentrice.   </span></em></strong></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; ">Cependant, le </span><strong><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">MCNP</span></strong><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; "> étant un Marché de Crédit en Nature Pérenne comme son nom l&rsquo;indique,  aucune créance n&rsquo;est due en espèce bancaire et reste en nature pour la simple  raison qu&rsquo;il n&rsquo; y a que les Biens, Produits et Services réels en demande qui  soldent de façon absolue les redevances. </span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:normal;text-autospace:none;"><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; ">En outre, le </span><strong><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:red; ">MCNP</span></strong><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; "> est conçu pour que personne ne doive à personne</span><span style="font-family:'Cambria','serif'; font-size:14.0pt; color:black; "> </span></p>
